<li>John Egerton, "<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://southernspaces.org/2009/walking-history-beginning-school-desegregation-nashville">Walking into History: The Beginning of School Desegregation in Nashville</a>," <i>Southern Spaces</i>, 4 May 2009, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="http://southernspaces.org/2009/walking-history-beginning-school-desegregation-nashville">southernspaces.org</a></li>
<li>Ruthie Yow, "<a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://southernspaces.org/2012/its-being-black-and-poor-race-class-and-desegregation-pebblebrook-high">'It's Being Black and Poor': Race, Class, and Desegregation at Pebblebrook High</a>," <i>Southern Spaces</i>, 20 February 2012, <a rel="nofollow" class="external text" href="https://southernspaces.org/2012/its-being-black-and-poor-race-class-and-desegregation-pebblebrook-high">southernspaces.org</a></li>
